<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Mastermind</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="stylesheets/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <div id="divTitle">
        <h1 class="title">elcome to Mastermind</h1>
      </div>

      <div id="codeMaker">
        CodeMaker</br>
        1. Make a code.</br>
        2. Wait for your opponent to guess your code.</br>
        3. Your opponent has 8 guesses.</br>
        4. If they can't break the code, you win.
      </div>

      <div id="codeBreaker">
        CodeBreaker</br>
        1. Wait for your opponent to make a code.</br>
        2. Guess the code made by the opponent.</br>
        3. You have 8 guesses.</br>
        4. If you break the code, you win.
      </div id="codeBreaker">

      <div id="startButton" onclick="location.href='http://localhost:3000/play'">
        Play game
      </div>

      <div id="statField">
        Statistics:</br>
          - x games currently being played.</br>
          - x players currently waiting in lobby</br>
          - x games played since last server restart.
			</div>
			
			<div id="colourSelectorSplash">
				<table>
					<tr><th class="pink" onclick="colourSelector('pink')">
						<!-- pink -->
					</th></tr>
					<tr><th class="green" onclick="colourSelector('green')">
						<!-- green -->
					</th></tr>
					<tr><th class="red" onclick="colourSelector('red')">
						<!-- red -->
					</th></tr>
					<tr><th class="blue" onclick="colourSelector('blue')">
						<!-- blue -->
					</th></tr>
				</table>
			</div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
